-//! Command history database for DCG.
-//!
-//! This module provides SQLite-based history collection and querying for
-//! tracking all commands evaluated by DCG across agent sessions.
-//!
-//! # Architecture
-//!
-//! ```text
-//! ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
